  },
  {
    "index": 1422,
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
    "string": "確か要救助者の１人、天川夏彦の母親の名前だ。"
  },
  {
    "index": 1427,
    "code": "0x45",
    "developer_comment": "渡瀬",
